WCL runs on x86 based machines running Linux 

See wcl.text for porting information.

INSTALLATION
------------

WCL is distributed in two parts - binaries and sources.

The binary distribution contains compiled libraries for the basic 
CL runtime and the compiler

Refer to wcl.text for more details.

DEBUGGING
---------

WGDB4-2 used to support WCL debugging under SunOS 4.X. It needs serious updating to be useful with current versions of GDB.

RESTRICTIONS
------------
WGDB does not yet support special WCL debugging features.


